      1          /**
      2           *  @file
      3           *
      4           *  @brief      Spi GDM module for STM32G0x implements the Spi Standard API (Application Programming Interface).
      5           *
      6           *  @details    This module provides the synchronous serial communication services to the application,
      7           *              such as initialization of Spi module, transmission/reception of byte and multiple bytes
      8           *              via Spi and status of Spi communication using Dma module
